snippet.textDisplay: It’s fitting that you refer to this person as “the nameless one”. There’s a similar case in Spain but it took about 20 years for the truth to come out. The victim - a woman - even lost her kids and was assaulted by her daughter through the manipulation of the abuser. Now when the victim talks about her abuser she refers to him as “este ser” (this being). - he doesn’t even deserve to be named. Seek the truth and justice but don’t feed the monster, not even by saying their name. Eventually the goal, after justice is served is to erase them from our collective consciousness - they feed of people, attention, causing pain, money and power, and controlling the narrative. When it becomes possible, shrink them into nothingness by ignoring them until they become the nameless one.

snippet.textDisplay:
YOUTUBE channels, please report the Depp vs Heard accurately with the right words and discontinue repetition of the same material. Johnny needs this!!

I am a feminist and am strongly opposed to any kind of abuse, but can’t stand behind Heard on this one!

Clearly I see that Depp has been abused by a narcissist. Why has no Youtube channels pointed out that Heard is highly MANIPULATIVE in recordings and she has set him up for ENTRAPMENT by recording him for years.

She undermines and gaslights him constantly, telling him he doesnt understand, and is the queen of word salad, dancing in circles, trying to put blame on him, while she is recording. Yet Depp is always patient, polite, doesnt take the bait, just is loving and wants peaceful closure.

She feeds him xanex while she is recording. She secretly videos him when she knows he will come home angry, repeatedly asking, “ you werent here this morning were you? ( probably at Elon Musks house and didnt take his calls) Totally set him up!!

She has had INFIDELITY with a couple guys while married to Depp. Elevator videos don’t lie.

It is also clear that she has abandonment issues, every time there was a confrontation Depp would leave, and that threw her into a anxiety and rage. Im sure all Heard’s exes knew about this experience with her.

To be fair, they had a toxic relationship (largely due to her insecurities) and the fact that they BOTH were drinking and using drugs more because they were both unhappy. They both need healing, she needs to heal her long-term abandonment issues and anger from her childhood. He needs to heal from recent narcissistic abuse, and question why he was a co-dependant for this type of person to begin with.

So Youtube channels, use the right words to define the scenerio, rather than repeating the same stuff over and over. Narcissist, Manipulative, Entrapment, Infidelity, Abandonment Issues, Addictions. These words will make a difference in court.

Johnny deserves better, and Im pretty sure he would agree with me on this!
